@node "Info" "Information On The Program"
SCSIPrefsMUI v1.0 was written in C and compiled using SAS/C 6.0.

   The source code was approximately 26K in size.
   The exeutable was approximately 14K in size.

MUIBuilder 2.1 was used to create the MUI interface and to set up some
notifications.

Heddley 1.1 was used, despite its constant desire to crash, to generate this
AmigaGuide document.               
@endnode

